{
  "name": "SparkHorizontalAxis",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkAxes/SparkAxes .htm#SparkAxes.SparkAxes\">SparkAxes</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkAxes/SparkAxes .htm#SparkAxes.Horizontal\">Horizontal</a></strong> 属性可返回迷你图组的 <strong>SparkHorizontalAxis</strong> 对象。水平轴只有在迷你图数据在垂直轴上同时有负值和正值的情况下才会显示。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴设置为可见，并设置该水平轴的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴绘制点的顺序，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightToLeftPlotOrder</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制点&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;按左至右顺序在水平轴上绘制点&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示一组迷你图的水平轴的设置。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Axis",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkColor/SparkColor .htm#SparkColor.SparkColor\">SparkColor</a></strong> 对象，该对象指定迷你图水平轴的颜色。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴的设置为不可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SparkColor",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "IsDateAxis",
      "summary": "<p>如果水平轴是基于日期值，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回迷你图的水平轴是否基于日期值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴是否基于日期值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsDateAxis</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴可见，则显示该水平轴是否基于日期值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsDateAxis</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong>Boolean</strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RightToLeftPlotOrder",
      "summary": "<p>将 <strong>RightToLeftPlotOrder</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>True</strong> 将按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置是否按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制点。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组是否按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightToLeftPlotOrder</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴设置为可见，并将该水平轴设置为按右至左顺序绘制点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightToLeftPlotOrder</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong>Boolean</strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}